// Alan wants to define a state machine where LED1 is switched on after a push on button B1
// and switched off 800ms after, waiting again for a new push on B1.

Sensor B1 on PIN0
Actuator LED1 on PIN1

initial ledOff {
    LED1 is LOW
    when B1 is HIGH then ledOn
}

ledOn {
    LED1 is HIGH
    after 800ms then ledOff
}